code: export async function fetchImageList(){const res=await fetch('http://220.149.235.221:4000/api/images');const fileList=await res.json();const sorted=fileList.filter(name=>name.startsWith('frame_')&&name.endsWith('.jpg')).sort((a,b)=>{const getTime=f=>{const match=f.match(/frame_(\d+)\.jpg/);return match?parseInt(match[1]):0;};return getTime(a)-getTime(b);});return sorted.map(name=>({name,url:`http://220.149.235.221:4000/images/${name}`,timestamp:parseInt(name.match(/frame_(\d+)\.jpg/)[1])}));}export async function fetchImageList_result(){const res=await fetch('http://220.149.235.221:4000/api/images_result');const fileList=await res.json();const sorted=fileList.filter(name=>name.endsWith('.jpg')).sort((a,b)=>{const getTime=f=>{const match=f.match(/frame(?:_result)?_(\d+)\.jpg/);return match?parseInt(match[1]):0;};return getTime(a)-getTime(b);});const fullData=sorted.map(name=>{const match=name.match(/frame(?:_result)?_(\d+)\.jpg/);return{name,url:`http://220.149.235.221:4000/images_result/${name}`,timestamp:match?parseInt(match[1]):0};});}
